          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bq-step" data-step="q6" data-key="q6" data-cat="schlaf">
          <h2 class="bq-question">Wie schläfst du?</h2>
          <ul class="bq-options" role="radiogroup">
            <li><button type="button" class="bq-option" data-answer="4"><span class="bq-option-marker">A</span><span>7 — 9 h, erholt</span></button></li>
            <li><button type="button" class="bq-option" data-answer="3"><span class="bq-option-marker">B</span><span>7 — 9 h, unruhig</span></button></li>
            <li><button type="button" class="bq-option" data-answer="2"><span class="bq-option-marker">C</span><span>5 — 7 h, meist ok</span></button></li>
            <li><button type="button" class="bq-option" data-answer="1"><span class="bq-option-marker">D</span><span>5 — 7 h, oft müde</span></button></li>
            <li><button type="button" class="bq-option" data-answer="0"><span class="bq-option-marker">E</span><span>Unter 5 h</span></button></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="bq-why">
            <span class="bq-why-label">Warum wir das fragen</span>
            Unter 6 Stunden Schlaf pro Nacht beschleunigen biologische Alterungsmarker messbar.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bq-step" data-step="q7" data-key="q7" data-cat="stress">
